{{Quote|I was not elected to watch my people suffer and die while you discuss this invasion in a committee!|Queen Amidala, to the Galactic Senate|audio=IWasNotElected-TPM.flac|<ref name="Episode 1">{{Film|I}}</ref>}}
The '''Galactic Senate Chamber''',<ref name="UltimateSW" /> also known as the '''Grand Convocation Chamber''',<ref name="Legends">''[[The Legends of Luke Skywalker]]''</ref> the '''Senate Rotunda''',<ref name="HC15">{{HelmetCollectionCite|15|Highlights of the Saga}}</ref> the '''grand audience chamber''',<ref name="Temptation of the Force">''[[The High Republic: Temptation of the Force]]''</ref> or simply as the '''Senate Chamber''',<ref name="Card Trader" /> was a large, open area contained within the [[Imperial Senate Building|Galactic Senate Building]] on the [[planet]] [[Coruscant]]. The chamber was the meeting hall for the [[Galactic Senate]] of the [[Galactic Republic]]<ref name="UltimateSW" /> and the center of political activity.<ref name="VE">''[[Star Wars: The Visual Encyclopedia]]''</ref>

It was lined with 1,024 [[repulsorpod]]s for the [[senator]]s and [[Junior Representative|representatives]] from the various political delegations,<ref name="UltimateSW" /><ref name="Galactic Atlas">''[[Star Wars: Galactic Atlas]]''</ref> with some delegations, such as the [[Naboo delegation]], having their own pod, while other representatives had to share.<ref name="VE" /> The platforms could detach from the walls of the chamber, which was equipped with voice-amplifying microphones, translators, and hovercams that recorded the various proceedings. At the center of the chamber was the [[Chancellor's Podium|Chancellor's podium]],<ref name="UltimateSW" /> itself extended from the "[[Chancellor's working office|working office]]" of the [[Chancellery Secretariat]],<ref name="CL2016">[[Star Wars: Complete Locations (2016)|''Star Wars: Complete Locations'']]</ref> where the [[Supreme Chancellor]] and the [[Vice Chair]] would preside over meetings of the Senate.

During the [[Clone Wars]], since the [[Infiltrator demolition droid]]s [[Bombing of Coruscant's central power distribution grid|blow up]] the [[central power distribution grid]] on [[Coruscant]] goes the [[Coruscant mandatory blackout|mandatory blackout]], even to stop the vote for the [[Republic financial reform bill|bill]] to de-regulate banking conglomerates, the repulsorpods and the chamber goes to the emergency power mode.<ref name="Heroes on Both Sides">{{TCW|Heroes on Both Sides}}</ref>

It was in the Galactic Senate Chamber that Chancellor [[Darth Sidious|Sheev Palpatine]] [[Proclamation of the New Order|proclaimed]] the formation of the [[Galactic Empire]] with himself as [[Galactic Emperor|emperor]] in front of the newly christened [[Imperial Senate]].<ref name="UltimateSW" /> Many of the repulsorpods were later damaged when Sidious and [[Jedi Master]] [[Yoda]] threw them at each other while [[Duel in the Galactic Senate|dueling]].<ref name="ROTS">{{Film|III}}</ref>

In the early [[Imperial Era]], the podium had changed and replaced the senate symbol with the [[Imperial crest]].<ref name="The Clone Conspiracy">{{TBB|The Clone Conspiracy}}</ref> During the Imperial Era, at the bottom of the podium, it replaced the symbol of the Republic with the Imperial crest,<ref name="Nobody's Listening">{{Andor|Nobody's Listening!}}</ref> and the repulsorpods had changed and added the Imperial crest.<ref name="Eye">{{Andor|The Eye}}</ref>

